1
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,960
=Adventure behind the Bronze Door=

2
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,900
(Adapted from the original novel
"Zang Hai Hua" by Nan Pai San Shu)

3
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:44,180
=Episode 31=
(This story is purely fictional)

4
00:02:17,580 --> 00:02:18,790
What's wrong?

5
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,320
I was wrong.

6
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:26,720
I was wrong about all of this.

7
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:32,600
I told you, don't look at anything.

8
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,089
Don't look at anything.

9
00:02:34,090 --> 00:02:35,900
If you look at anything,
you'll get into trouble.

10
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:38,070
What's going on?

11
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,200
It won't be.

12
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,360
No.

13
00:02:44,690 --> 00:02:46,390
Are you done with this,

14
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:47,480
Wu Xie?

15
00:02:48,650 --> 00:02:50,360
It's all over now.

16
00:02:50,810 --> 00:02:52,040
What's it?

17
00:02:58,530 --> 00:03:00,510
Why do I have to watch it?

18
00:03:02,740 --> 00:03:04,640
Someone will finish it.

19
00:03:05,370 --> 00:03:08,070
How could anyone possibly finish it?

20
00:03:08,490 --> 00:03:10,299
When the time comes, give the tape

21
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:12,670
to anyone who's worked with me
for more than three years.

22
00:03:13,210 --> 00:03:14,230
This guy

23
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:15,920
can definitely do it.

24
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,640
What's wrong with this?

25
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,390
Wasn't he talking about you?

26
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,910
I've been complimenting you
all night. What else do you want?

27
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:28,510
If Zanghai Flower Field is
to be destroyed once in many years,

28
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:31,489
Qiling destroyed it

29
00:03:31,490 --> 00:03:33,070
before the last time limit.

30
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:35,689
Because the time
of Tianshou was uncertain,

31
00:03:35,690 --> 00:03:36,769
he was afraid

32
00:03:36,770 --> 00:03:39,440
that he would forget about it
during the next Tianshou,

33
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:41,649
so he made a video saying

34
00:03:41,650 --> 00:03:43,270
that he would appoint someone

35
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:45,179
to destroy Zanghai Flower Field for him

36
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:47,040
before the next 80 years came.

37
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:50,760
Later, Zhang Haike
intercepted the tape.

38
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,809
You're the one

39
00:03:52,810 --> 00:03:53,739
the patriarch chose.

40
00:03:53,740 --> 00:03:55,689
It was at this point in time

41
00:03:55,690 --> 00:03:56,649
that he found

42
00:03:56,650 --> 00:03:59,179
the most possible person
to be Qiling's proxy,

43
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:00,360
namely me,

44
00:04:00,370 --> 00:04:01,920
to fulfill this mission.

45
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:05,179
I'll go back and find you a psychiatrist

46
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,760
to help you forget about it.

47
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:10,079
Why did Qiling say that this person
must be able to do it?

48
00:04:10,079 --> 00:04:12,059
What kind of conditions
does this person have to meet?

49
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:13,459
Okay, let me make it clear to you.

50
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,179
Firstly,

51
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:15,419
this person has to believe him

52
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:16,739
after watching the video, right?

53
00:04:16,740 --> 00:04:17,569
Secondly,

54
00:04:17,570 --> 00:04:20,110
Wang Jinyuan believes this person

55
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:22,979
believes Qiling and knows Qiling well.

56
00:04:22,980 --> 00:04:23,889
It's you, isn't it?

57
00:04:23,890 --> 00:04:25,179
And thirdly? Is there more?

58
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:26,739
This person must have Dragon's Plasma.

59
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:28,739
Or he can't open the door
to Zanghai Flower Field.

60
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:30,569
I got this fake Dragon's Plasma

61
00:04:30,570 --> 00:04:31,979
at Seven Stars Lu Palace.

62
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:35,059
It was our first adventure and
I accidentally consumed Dragon's Blood.

63
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,659
It was a complete accident

64
00:04:36,660 --> 00:04:38,920
and it was after Qiling made the video.

65
00:04:39,450 --> 00:04:41,009
If you hadn't eaten Dragon's Blood,

66
00:04:41,010 --> 00:04:42,750
you wouldn't be the proxy.

67
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:44,329
How could Qiling have foreseen

68
00:04:44,330 --> 00:04:46,160
that I would accidentally
consume Dragon's Blood?

69
00:05:03,540 --> 00:05:04,870
The truth of the matter is

70
00:05:07,130 --> 00:05:09,159
that Qiling simply couldn't have

71
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,929
foreseen that many years later
there would be someone

72
00:05:11,930 --> 00:05:13,960
who fits all the criteria.

73
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:17,310
That means the proxy doesn't exist.

74
00:05:17,490 --> 00:05:19,280
We've been tricked.

75
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:23,080
Who is he

76
00:05:23,330 --> 00:05:24,990
recording this video for?

77
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:29,080
If this proxy doesn't exist,

78
00:05:30,570 --> 00:05:31,369
this tape

79
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:33,160
wasn't meant for me.

80
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:36,840
It's also a mechanism.

81
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:39,360
It's what Qiling keeps for himself.

82
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:41,990
A mechanism to remind himself.

83
00:05:46,780 --> 00:05:48,430
Even Yu Da's wrong.

84
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:52,310
He said I'm the chosen one,

85
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,630
but I'm not.

86
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:57,430
It's Qiling himself.

87
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,430
For so long,

88
00:06:05,890 --> 00:06:07,870
Qiling has always been alone.

89
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:10,670
For such an important mission,

90
00:06:11,330 --> 00:06:13,630
he had to make a video tape
to remind himself,

91
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:16,110
and he couldn't even find someone
to give a word to.

92
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:22,790
It's not a clever trick at all.

93
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:25,790
In the old days,

94
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:28,040
I would have recognised it immediately.

95
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:30,670
And along the way,

96
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:33,190
I've had plenty of chances

97
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:35,600
to expose their flaws.

98
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:41,040
But because of the obsession
I have in my heart with Qiling's past,

99
00:06:41,810 --> 00:06:43,670
it affects all my judgments.

100
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:47,670
Zhang Haike also took advantage of this

101
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:50,750
and led me step by step
to where I am today.

102
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:56,720
Okay. It's fine.

103
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:59,280
I treat you the same way, don't I?

104
00:06:59,690 --> 00:07:00,659
All these years,

105
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:03,080
I've been with you, pretending
to be a fool and being tricked.

106
00:07:04,660 --> 00:07:05,960
That's what

107
00:07:06,570 --> 00:07:08,630
I'm willing to do, isn't it?

108
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,160
I got it.

109
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,489
Fine.

110
00:07:13,490 --> 00:07:14,859
Anyway, we're going back tomorrow.

111
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:15,840
Come on.

112
00:07:15,930 --> 00:07:17,080
Drink up.

113
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:19,520
Before we go back to Wuzhou,

114
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:21,230
let's go to the spiritual retreat

115
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:22,920
to say goodbye to Qiling.

116
00:07:45,330 --> 00:07:46,400
Sir.

117
00:07:48,450 --> 00:07:49,630
What a coincidence.

118
00:07:50,330 --> 00:07:52,230
I was just going
for a walk down the hill.

119
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,280
Mister,

120
00:07:54,330 --> 00:07:56,360
have you finished your business here?

121
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:57,489
Yes,

122
00:07:57,490 --> 00:07:58,929
I have.

123
00:07:58,930 --> 00:08:00,400
We're going back to Wuzhou.

124
00:08:00,930 --> 00:08:02,360
We came to say goodbye to him,

125
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:04,249
and to look at the previous scrolls.

126
00:08:04,250 --> 00:08:06,929
I found a few more scrolls last night

127
00:08:06,930 --> 00:08:09,430
and put them in Zhang Qiling's room.

128
00:08:15,450 --> 00:08:16,630
That's a lot.

129
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:20,110
Qiling's just a painting seller.

130
00:08:21,010 --> 00:08:23,059
Anyway, the matter
of Zanghai Flower is settled,

131
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:24,630
and we have plenty of time now.

132
00:08:24,690 --> 00:08:26,099
I just wonder

133
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:28,280
what kind of message he left this time.

134
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:33,990
Just take a look.

135
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:35,870
Good luck with your new discovery.

136
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:47,390
Fatty,

137
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:49,800
look.

138
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:51,179
This drawing

139
00:08:51,180 --> 00:08:53,630
seems to show the origin
of the Zhang family.

140
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:56,499
The origin of the Zhang family

141
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,990
is a lump of carbon?

142
00:08:58,140 --> 00:08:59,270
Meteoric copper.

143
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:02,480
You know that?

144
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:03,910
Tell me about it.

145
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,929
I've always thought

146
00:09:06,930 --> 00:09:08,680
that the Zhang family system
was complicated,

147
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:11,230
but now that I've seen this drawing,

148
00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:14,200
it seems like I can figure it out.

149
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:16,610
The mystical power of the hexagonal bell
and the Heavenly Staff

150
00:09:16,610 --> 00:09:18,200
is derived from the meteoric copper.

151
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:20,139
The Zhang family's mystical power

152
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:21,870
also comes from meteoric copper.

153
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:23,720
And Zhang Haike told me

154
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:26,000
about the reason for the
hexagonal bell's hallucinogenic effect.

155
00:09:29,930 --> 00:09:31,499
The ringing is just a cover-up.

156
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:32,990
It's the powder

157
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:34,750
that really does the trick.

158
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:37,600
Look, is it possible?

159
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:41,320
There are two kinds of parasites

160
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:43,720
in this meteoric copper
from outer space.

161
00:09:44,180 --> 00:09:46,089
The parasites in the red meteoric copper

162
00:09:46,090 --> 00:09:46,929
are called red bugs,

163
00:09:46,930 --> 00:09:49,899
and the parasites in the blue meteoric
copper is called blue bugs.

164
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:52,390
One is called Blue,

165
00:09:52,730 --> 00:09:54,969
one is called Red,

166
00:09:54,970 --> 00:09:57,480
and those outside are called Black.

167
00:09:57,810 --> 00:09:58,899
So the Zhangs

168
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:00,659
are in trouble with the bugs.

169
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,800
Go on.

170
00:10:02,266 --> 00:10:04,809
Blue bugs have been parasitising
the Zhangs for a long time.

171
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:05,849
Blue bugs give the Zhangs

172
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:07,360
extraordinary abilities.

173
00:10:07,490 --> 00:10:08,729
At the same time, they discovered

174
00:10:08,730 --> 00:10:10,999
that the secretion of blue bugs
can make people hallucinogenic.

175
00:10:10,999 --> 00:10:12,929
So they made a hexagonal bell
out of meteoric copper

176
00:10:12,930 --> 00:10:14,499
parasitised with blue bugs.

177
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,089
Whenever the bell is rung,

178
00:10:16,090 --> 00:10:17,929
the secretion
of blue bugs will float out

179
00:10:17,930 --> 00:10:19,209
and make people hallucinate.

180
00:10:19,210 --> 00:10:21,659
But because the Zhangs
have blue bugs in their bodies,

181
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:23,779
they have antibodies,

182
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:25,200
so they won't be affected.

183
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:26,729
And on the Heavenly Staff are red bugs.

184
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:28,329
These red bugs are highly intelligent

185
00:10:28,330 --> 00:10:29,840
and can influence the blue bugs.

186
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:33,329
When the Heavenly Staff activates
the mechanism in Zhang Family Ancient Tower,

187
00:10:33,330 --> 00:10:35,089
the red bugs will be activated,

188
00:10:35,090 --> 00:10:37,539
emitting specific pheromones

189
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:39,499
and exchanging pheromones
with the blue bugs

190
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:41,449
living in the Zhang family's bodies.

191
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:42,659
In nature,

192
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:43,899
many bugs

193
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:45,870
communicate in this way.

194
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:48,609
After the exchange,
a special substance is secreted

195
00:10:48,610 --> 00:10:50,750
that affects the Zhangs' brains

196
00:10:50,810 --> 00:10:52,569
and manipulates their behaviour.

197
00:10:52,570 --> 00:10:56,030
This is what the Zhangs call Tianshou.

198
00:10:56,810 --> 00:10:58,539
You mean

199
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,990
that when Red and Blue mate,

200
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:02,440
the Zhangs' disease flares up?

201
00:11:03,570 --> 00:11:05,230
That's a good way to put it.

202
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:08,600
So the impressive Zhang family

203
00:11:08,773 --> 00:11:10,863
is being played
by these two kinds of bugs.

204
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:13,139
In fact,
it's the Zhang family's patriarch

205
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:14,560
who's really controlling all this.

206
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:16,080
The Zhang family members

207
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,569
who first invented the use of bugs
to control the clan's Tianshou

208
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:21,150
left the antidote
in Zhang Family Ancient Tower.

209
00:11:21,210 --> 00:11:22,960
Only the patriarch knows the secret.

210
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,079
But successive generations
of Zhang family patriarchs

211
00:11:26,079 --> 00:11:27,969
chose to continue controlling the clan

212
00:11:27,970 --> 00:11:29,270
in this way

213
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:31,990
until the appearance of Qiling.

214
00:11:33,140 --> 00:11:34,729
If the Heavenly Staff is activated,

215
00:11:34,730 --> 00:11:36,539
Qiling will suffer a seizure

216
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:38,510
and lose control of his brain.

217
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:39,960
Tianshou

218
00:11:40,210 --> 00:11:42,870
will make him forget the way
to remove it,

219
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:47,510
so Qiling can save all the Zhangs

220
00:11:47,970 --> 00:11:49,990
but not himself.

221
00:11:50,260 --> 00:11:53,569
Though he never wanted
to save himself either.

222
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:56,630
That's why he's our Qiling.

223
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:57,729
Anyway, Naive,

224
00:11:57,730 --> 00:12:00,330
You've explained everything

225
00:12:00,330 --> 00:12:02,179
but there's still one thing
that doesn't make sense.

226
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:05,510
If the Zhangs can't be affected
by hallucinations,

227
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:08,449
how can the hexagonal bell
make Zhang Haixing

228
00:12:08,450 --> 00:12:09,870
hallucinate?

229
00:12:09,930 --> 00:12:11,259
When the Zhangs

230
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:13,200
drank the water from the well,

231
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,019
the blue bugs
in their bodies were killed

232
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:17,270
and they lost their immunity
to hallucinations.

233
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:20,320
But to save Niata, Zhang Haike

234
00:12:20,330 --> 00:12:23,960
used the forbidden hexagonal bell again.

235
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:26,569
That's why they can accidentally

236
00:12:26,570 --> 00:12:28,969
get infected by the secretions
of the blue bugs

237
00:12:28,970 --> 00:12:30,560
and hallucinate.

238
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:33,379
I didn't expect Zhang Haike

239
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:35,209
to be such a passionate man.

240
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:36,929
There's one more thing I've figured out.

241
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:38,499
Why does the blood of some of the Zhangs

242
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,659
repel bugs?

243
00:12:39,660 --> 00:12:41,689
Could it be because the worms

244
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:44,179
can sense the special substance
secreted by the red bugs

245
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:46,539
in the blood of the Zhangs,

246
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:48,200
so they just avoid it?

247
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:50,019
Amazing.

248
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:51,539
You took three minutes

249
00:12:51,540 --> 00:12:53,800
to explain the family history

250
00:12:53,850 --> 00:12:55,600
of the Zhangs.

251
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:01,960
So these are the problems

252
00:13:03,330 --> 00:13:04,809
that Qiling must endure

253
00:13:04,810 --> 00:13:06,230
and solve.

254
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,320
Most of the world's secrets

255
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:11,680
are here.

256
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:13,729
That's why he has to enter

257
00:13:13,730 --> 00:13:15,630
Bronze Door again and again

258
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:17,440
to solve these problems.

259
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:39,510
Have some.

260
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:49,230
(After reading the scrolls,)

261
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:51,630
(I finally got
the whole story straight.)

262
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:54,560
(Zanghai Flower is innocent.)

263
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:56,560
(It's not the seeds of Zanghai Flower)

264
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:58,720
(that really drove
the Mystic Claw crazy,)

265
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:01,360
(it's these golden sphere bugs.)

266
00:14:02,660 --> 00:14:03,689
(I guessed wrong)

267
00:14:03,690 --> 00:14:04,990
(when I looked at the mural.)

268
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:07,800
(Zhang Haixing and the others'
speculation was also wrong.)

269
00:14:08,260 --> 00:14:09,870
(According to the scrolls,)

270
00:14:10,090 --> 00:14:11,480
(a long time ago,)

271
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:14,154
(the Zhang family accidentally
discovered Zanghai Flower)

272
00:14:14,155 --> 00:14:16,320
(while investigating
a strange incident.)

273
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:18,800
(That area was special.)

274
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:22,200
(Zanghai Flower
could only survive there.)

275
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:24,560
(So a field of Zanghai Flower Field)

276
00:14:24,660 --> 00:14:26,910
(was created there.)

277
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,440
(But unexpectedly,)

278
00:14:29,690 --> 00:14:30,299
(there was)

279
00:14:30,300 --> 00:14:32,230
(a golden sphere-shaped creature
in that place.)

280
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:34,230
(The creature)

281
00:14:34,450 --> 00:14:36,560
(seems to come
from deep within the earth,)

282
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:38,089
(and it's ever-present)

283
00:14:38,090 --> 00:14:39,440
(and impossible to eradicate.)

284
00:14:39,810 --> 00:14:41,750
(They have a parasitic habit
when they're young.)

285
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:44,200
(On other organisms.)

286
00:14:45,450 --> 00:14:46,750
(This parasitism)

287
00:14:46,850 --> 00:14:48,840
(is very damaging to the host.)

288
00:14:49,500 --> 00:14:51,200
(With the exception of Zanghai Flower,)

289
00:14:51,210 --> 00:14:53,030
(all other parasitised organisms)

290
00:14:53,610 --> 00:14:56,150
(undergo some degree of mutation,)

291
00:14:56,330 --> 00:14:57,990
(which is very dangerous.)

292
00:14:58,060 --> 00:14:59,990
(Much of the information in the scrolls)

293
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,200
(is actually shown on the murals.)

294
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:05,449
(The small snakes left in the ruins)

295
00:15:05,450 --> 00:15:06,990
(of the Mystic Claw and Kumuli)

296
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:09,390
(were mutated)

297
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:12,630
(because they were parasitised
by the golden sphere bugs.)

298
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:16,870
(Those golden spheres we encountered
at Snowy Peak)

299
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:19,080
(are the adults of that species.)

300
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:21,870
(When they mature,
they can survive independently)

301
00:15:21,900 --> 00:15:23,320
(from their hosts)

302
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:25,800
(and are very aggressive.)

303
00:15:27,810 --> 00:15:30,230
(When the Zhangs hunted
for snakes in Kumuli,)

304
00:15:30,730 --> 00:15:33,080
(they were actually dealing
with the golden sphere bugs.)

305
00:15:34,373 --> 00:15:36,593
(The golden spheres
have no medicinal value.)

306
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:39,720
(The golden sphere caught by the Denaxi)

307
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:42,089
(was tested for its medicinal value)

308
00:15:42,090 --> 00:15:44,539
(because it had harmed
the Zhang family member, Dong Chan.)

309
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:46,910
(And the so-called medicinal value)

310
00:15:46,930 --> 00:15:49,840
(is supposed to come
from the blue bugs in Zhangs' body.)

311
00:15:50,940 --> 00:15:52,969
(In order to prevent the golden spheres
from spreading)

312
00:15:52,970 --> 00:15:54,960
(and causing serious harm,)

313
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:56,809
(the Zhangs built a huge bronze door)

314
00:15:56,810 --> 00:15:58,960
(outside the flower field.)

315
00:16:00,090 --> 00:16:02,030
(But the golden spheres breed too fast.)

316
00:16:02,090 --> 00:16:03,449
(Every 80 years,)

317
00:16:03,450 --> 00:16:05,480
(they could flood the field)

318
00:16:05,850 --> 00:16:08,080
(with ripe Zanghai Flower seeds)

319
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:11,110
(and spread beyond
Zanghai Flower Field.)

320
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:13,390
(That's why the Zhang family
set up a trap)

321
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,419
(to kill the little golden sphere bugs)

322
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:17,299
(parasitised on Zanghai Flower)

323
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:18,720
(by eliminating them)

324
00:16:18,730 --> 00:16:20,019
(and asked their descendants)

325
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:21,539
(to come to Zanghai Flower Field)

326
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:23,870
(every 80 years to deal with them.)

327
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:28,150
(After the Zhang family fell apart,)

328
00:16:28,970 --> 00:16:31,089
(Zanghai Flower Field
was left unmanaged.)

329
00:16:31,090 --> 00:16:33,360
(Beyond this time limit,)

330
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:35,569
(the little golden sphere bugs
were rapidly growing)

331
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:37,320
(and flowing out
of Zanghai Flower Field.)

332
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:41,510
(The Mystic Claw in armor could have dealt
with the golden spheres.)

333
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:43,720
(But when the armor
fell into disrepair,)

334
00:16:43,970 --> 00:16:46,480
(the Mystic Claw went berserk,)

335
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:48,139
(causing a great deal of damage)

336
00:16:48,140 --> 00:16:50,200
(to Yinshaluo Tribe.)

337
00:16:51,020 --> 00:16:51,960
(After that,)

338
00:16:52,090 --> 00:16:53,800
(Qiling arrived here)

339
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:56,110
(and got rid of the Mystic Claw
and activated the mechanism)

340
00:16:56,260 --> 00:16:58,800
(to destroy the little golden
spheres bugs in the flower field.)

341
00:16:59,330 --> 00:17:01,569
(But they won't be wiped out
completely.)

342
00:17:01,570 --> 00:17:03,150
(That's why Qiling)

343
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:05,699
(has to come here again after 80 years)

344
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:07,320
(to activate the mechanism.)

345
00:17:07,370 --> 00:17:09,939
(Fearing that he'd forget the matter)

346
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:11,430
(due to his frequent memory loss,)

347
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:14,870
(he left himself a video tape
as a reminder.)

348
00:17:15,090 --> 00:17:16,870
(Unexpectedly, by accident,)

349
00:17:17,370 --> 00:17:20,040
(I ended up carrying out the mission.)

350
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:23,150
(But thankfully,)

351
00:17:23,570 --> 00:17:25,299
(the mechanism of Zanghai Flower Field)

352
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:28,080
(kills only
the little golden sphere bugs.)

353
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:29,649
(Someday,)

354
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:31,430
(Zanghai Flower)

355
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:33,110
(will grow back.)

356
00:17:56,090 --> 00:17:57,280
(The Zhangs)

357
00:17:57,410 --> 00:18:00,240
(had been researching the function
of Zanghai Flower Field,)

358
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:03,470
(and found
that once the flowers were picked,)

359
00:18:03,570 --> 00:18:05,670
(they withered quickly)

360
00:18:05,980 --> 00:18:07,870
(and the seeds were inactivated.)

361
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:10,760
(The medicine made from it)

362
00:18:10,850 --> 00:18:12,630
(only protects people from death,)

363
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:14,560
(and is stored away.)

364
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,910
(The Zhang family has done an
excellent job of keeping secrets.)

365
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:25,110
(Except for the core members,)

366
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,950
(no one knows the truth
about Zanghai Flower.)

367
00:18:29,610 --> 00:18:31,630
(After the Zhang family fell apart,)

368
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:34,110
(the transmission
of the core secrets was interrupted.)

369
00:18:34,650 --> 00:18:36,499
(Zhang Haike
and other outside family members)

370
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:38,600
(don't know the secret.)

371
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:42,320
(In fact, Zanghai Flower)

372
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:45,110
(is a very precious herb)

373
00:18:45,370 --> 00:18:47,910
(that can strengthen
the Zhang family's constitution,)

374
00:18:48,540 --> 00:18:50,840
(and maybe
there's a special way to use it.)

375
00:18:51,260 --> 00:18:53,950
(But it has no power
to bring the dead back to life.)

376
00:18:56,890 --> 00:18:59,280
(Zhang Haike has been pursuing it
for many years.)

377
00:18:59,940 --> 00:19:01,670
(But his obsession is so strong)

378
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:03,630
(that he can be easily used.)

379
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:06,430
(Behind the whole thing)

380
00:19:06,610 --> 00:19:08,329
(is the mysterious family)

381
00:19:08,330 --> 00:19:11,040
(that's hiding in the darkness
and pushing the envelope.)

382
00:19:12,060 --> 00:19:13,000
(This family)

383
00:19:13,810 --> 00:19:16,560
(has been fighting the Zhangs
for thousands of years.)

384
00:19:16,650 --> 00:19:18,080
(It's the Zhang family's)

385
00:19:18,540 --> 00:19:20,560
(and Zhang Qiling's archenemy.)

386
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:32,470
Fatty.

387
00:19:33,170 --> 00:19:34,840
Fatty, wake up.

388
00:19:35,130 --> 00:19:36,560
Time for breakfast?

389
00:19:42,220 --> 00:19:43,430
Finished?

390
00:19:44,610 --> 00:19:46,240
What did you find out?

391
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,670
Let's go say goodbye to Qiling

392
00:19:49,090 --> 00:19:50,710
and get ready to go back to Wuzhou.

393
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:53,470
We've got a lot of work ahead of us.

394
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:01,190
Qiling,

395
00:20:02,780 --> 00:20:04,390
Fatty and I

396
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:06,950
have taken care of this mission for you.

397
00:20:07,650 --> 00:20:08,870
Don't worry.

398
00:20:10,700 --> 00:20:11,870
When you get out,

399
00:20:12,850 --> 00:20:13,609
we'll establish

400
00:20:13,610 --> 00:20:15,520
the anchoring point
between you and the world.

401
00:20:17,060 --> 00:20:18,569
Although

402
00:20:18,570 --> 00:20:21,259
you are your own chosen one in the end,

403
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:23,409
after this incident,

404
00:20:23,410 --> 00:20:25,280
Naive and I

405
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:27,089
are already qualified

406
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:29,129
to become your chosen ones.

407
00:20:29,130 --> 00:20:31,219
We've saved

408
00:20:31,220 --> 00:20:33,430
your face for once.

409
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:36,360
Wait another five years.

410
00:20:36,740 --> 00:20:38,040
You must

411
00:20:38,170 --> 00:20:39,329
live a long life.

412
00:20:39,330 --> 00:20:40,390
Great luck.

413
00:20:41,610 --> 00:20:43,089
Great fortune.

414
00:20:43,090 --> 00:20:46,190
We'll see you then.

