00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:05,110
Sir.

418
00:21:07,610 --> 00:21:08,910
Come on.

419
00:21:09,540 --> 00:21:10,539
Come in and sit down.

420
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:11,459
No,

421
00:21:11,460 --> 00:21:13,040
we came to say goodbye.

422
00:21:13,370 --> 00:21:15,110
We're really leaving this time.

423
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,539
Sit down for a while.

424
00:21:16,540 --> 00:21:18,219
I have something to tell you.

425
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:19,089
Come on.

426
00:21:19,090 --> 00:21:21,539
Don't tell me there's a new scroll.

427
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:22,809
It's over.

428
00:21:22,810 --> 00:21:23,939
We really should go. Let's go.

429
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:24,889
Come on.

430
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:26,520
There's no rush. Come on.

431
00:21:26,610 --> 00:21:27,840
Sit down for a while.

432
00:21:28,890 --> 00:21:29,950
No.

433
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:43,240
It's too much of a drag.

434
00:21:47,330 --> 00:21:48,840
It's not cooked yet.

435
00:21:51,410 --> 00:21:53,430
What's your plan for the future?

436
00:21:54,410 --> 00:21:56,710
There's something very important
waiting for us.

437
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:59,040
I've got a

438
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:01,110
little advice.

439
00:22:01,700 --> 00:22:02,870
Please go ahead.

440
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:04,800
Stay

441
00:22:04,940 --> 00:22:06,360
and be Deren.

442
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:09,169
30,000 yuan a month,

443
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:10,360
food and lodging included.

444
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,739
The Zhangs

445
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:13,219
don't have any work now.

446
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:15,110
It's very easy.

447
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:18,779
So the Zhang family
is a multinational corporation,

448
00:22:18,780 --> 00:22:20,000
so rich.

449
00:22:20,940 --> 00:22:23,089
We had been doing a lot
of odd jobs for Qiling,

450
00:22:23,090 --> 00:22:24,840
and he didn't pay us a cent.

451
00:22:25,170 --> 00:22:27,569
Qiling is even more shady than you,
the shady boss.

452
00:22:27,570 --> 00:22:28,870
To be precise,

453
00:22:29,170 --> 00:22:31,779
some years ago, it was Qiling
who did odd jobs for us

454
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:33,320
and cleaned up our messes for us.

455
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:36,470
So he's still the most shady one.

456
00:22:36,570 --> 00:22:37,569
Here you go.

457
00:22:37,570 --> 00:22:38,870
Try this.

458
00:22:39,570 --> 00:22:40,710
Thank you.

459
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:44,110
Wu Xie,

460
00:22:45,170 --> 00:22:46,390
you're the man

461
00:22:46,810 --> 00:22:48,800
for the position, Deren.

462
00:22:48,850 --> 00:22:50,040
Look,

463
00:22:50,940 --> 00:22:53,710
Deren has been vacant for years.

464
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:56,910
You are here at the right time.

465
00:22:57,220 --> 00:23:00,040
And you have a deep connection

466
00:23:00,090 --> 00:23:02,110
with Zhang Qiling.

467
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:05,360
As long as you're Deren,

468
00:23:05,570 --> 00:23:08,219
you can continue to take your time

469
00:23:08,220 --> 00:23:11,600
and study about him in the future.

470
00:23:11,810 --> 00:23:14,670
If he comes back one day,

471
00:23:15,130 --> 00:23:16,369
you can still

472
00:23:16,370 --> 00:23:20,080
record his memories.

473
00:23:20,610 --> 00:23:21,699
Isn't that

474
00:23:21,700 --> 00:23:23,280
two birds with one stone?

475
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:28,870
We've gone over all the information.

476
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:31,080
