00:23:43,700 --> 00:23:45,499
I'm very rigorous.

483
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:46,630
Besides,

484
00:23:46,780 --> 00:23:49,569
we have high expectations

485
00:23:49,570 --> 00:23:50,870
of Deren.

486
00:23:53,700 --> 00:23:54,760
Wu Xie,

487
00:23:55,850 --> 00:23:57,470
you're strong-minded

488
00:23:57,810 --> 00:23:59,569
and meticulous.

489
00:23:59,570 --> 00:24:02,630
If you're going to take
on the position of Deren,

490
00:24:02,650 --> 00:24:04,739
it'll be the result

491
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:06,670
of causality.

492
00:24:07,890 --> 00:24:09,470
I'll be relieved

493
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:11,280
if you stay.

494
00:24:15,700 --> 00:24:16,870
I got it.

495
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:20,600
You want to go out and have fun?

496
00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:22,089
(Newspaper)
Travel guide.

497
00:24:22,090 --> 00:24:24,000
You're picking out the best land
in the world.

498
00:24:24,890 --> 00:24:27,760
You're looking for a replacement,

499
00:24:28,090 --> 00:24:30,169
a second-hand Deren, aren't you?

500
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:32,040
I'm not going out to have fun,

501
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:35,390
I'm going traveling.

502
00:24:36,370 --> 00:24:37,459
Tell me more about it.

503
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:40,040
Spiritual practice

504
00:24:40,500 --> 00:24:42,710
can't be limited to a single place.

505
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:46,840
We must go out into the crowd

506
00:24:47,330 --> 00:24:50,499
to gain a deeper understanding.

507
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:51,670
Anyway,

508
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:53,280
we can't leave

509
00:24:54,090 --> 00:24:56,710
the spiritual retreat unattended,
can we?

510
00:24:58,650 --> 00:25:02,569
You don't have to tell us
about your spiritual practice,

511
00:25:02,570 --> 00:25:05,870
you can just say I want to retire

512
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:07,840
and go around the world.

513
00:25:07,890 --> 00:25:09,630
We all understand.

514
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,409
You're so old, aren't you?

515
00:25:11,410 --> 00:25:13,760
It's only right to enjoy your old age.

516
00:25:14,330 --> 00:25:16,390
Here you go.

517
00:25:16,700 --> 00:25:17,950
Keep it.

518
00:25:19,410 --> 00:25:20,840
30,000 yuan, right?

519
00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:22,430
30,000 yuan.

520
00:25:22,810 --> 00:25:24,000
It's not a small amount.

521
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:26,129
That's

522
00:25:26,130 --> 00:25:27,649
as many ham sausages

523
00:25:27,650 --> 00:25:29,600
as you want in one meal.

524
00:25:30,890 --> 00:25:33,649
Can Deren resign?

525
00:25:33,650 --> 00:25:34,870
No.

526
00:25:35,740 --> 00:25:38,569
Deren is for life.

527
00:25:38,570 --> 00:25:42,000
Once you take on the job,
you have to stay on for life.

528
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:44,240
Unless he dies of old age

529
00:25:46,170 --> 00:25:47,430
or

530
00:25:48,170 --> 00:25:49,369
someone else takes his place.

531
00:25:49,370 --> 00:25:51,649
No one can take on this job.

532
00:25:51,650 --> 00:25:52,979
Not for any amount of money.

533
00:25:52,980 --> 00:25:54,840
No freedom, no way.

534
00:25:55,650 --> 00:25:57,800
Please let us go.

535
00:25:57,980 --> 00:25:59,240
Stop talking about Deren.

536
00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:02,630
If you two

537
00:26:03,570 --> 00:26:05,240
decide to leave,

538
00:26:05,330 --> 00:26:07,560
leaving this spiritual retreat,

539
00:26:08,300 --> 00:26:09,609
you'll go back

540
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:11,710
to your old lives.

541
00:26:12,570 --> 00:26:14,040
The world is like the sea.

542
00:26:15,130 --> 00:26:16,320
A man

543
00:26:17,300 --> 00:26:19,080
is like a grain of sand,

544
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:22,150
once it enters the sea,

545
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:25,320
it can never return.

546
00:26:25,850 --> 00:26:26,950
Misters,

547
00:26:27,810 --> 00:26:29,630
think about it again.

548
00:26:44,370 --> 00:26:45,950
Thank you for your kind offer.

549
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,040
It's just that there's still

550
00:26:50,330 --> 00:26:52,150
my unfinished business in the crowd.

