00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:55,040
If it's meant to be,

552
00:26:55,410 --> 00:26:57,080
we'll meet again.

553
00:26:57,610 --> 00:26:58,800
You said

554
00:26:59,810 --> 00:27:01,560
our karmic line is still long.

555
00:27:02,850 --> 00:27:04,280
All right, that's it.

556
00:27:04,850 --> 00:27:06,040
Wait.

557
00:27:06,850 --> 00:27:08,889
We really have to go home.

558
00:27:08,890 --> 00:27:10,849
We haven't been home for a long time.

559
00:27:10,850 --> 00:27:12,710
It's fine that you won't
take on the position.

560
00:27:13,090 --> 00:27:15,760
It's fate that we met.

561
00:27:16,410 --> 00:27:18,219
Before you go,

562
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:20,870
I have something to give you.

563
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:23,520
One for each of you.

564
00:27:30,650 --> 00:27:31,739
You're being

565
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:33,059
too particular.

566
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:34,569
You're being too courteous.

567
00:27:34,570 --> 00:27:36,219
We're embarrassed.

568
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,569
Don't get too much for us.

569
00:27:37,570 --> 00:27:38,950
Just get one.

570
00:27:42,170 --> 00:27:43,320
Well...

571
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,870
Come on, take it.

572
00:27:46,410 --> 00:27:47,520
This is yours.

573
00:27:48,980 --> 00:27:50,360
No, this...

574
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:57,609
The more insignificant something is,

575
00:27:57,610 --> 00:28:00,390
the more secret it contains.

576
00:28:00,650 --> 00:28:01,569
Let me ask you.

577
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:04,430
Is there a trick of fortune,

578
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:07,390
secret manual or treasure in it?

579
00:28:07,810 --> 00:28:09,280
Let me see yours.

580
00:28:11,410 --> 00:28:13,110
There's nothing.

581
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:13,889
What do you mean?

582
00:28:13,890 --> 00:28:15,390
Are you fooling us?

583
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:19,040
Both of you are men of action

584
00:28:19,810 --> 00:28:21,390
who have a mission

585
00:28:21,850 --> 00:28:23,600
and a long way to go.

586
00:28:25,020 --> 00:28:27,710
It's a spiritual practice

587
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:30,320
for you to read the scrolls here,

588
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:33,320
and it's a spiritual practice for you

589
00:28:33,610 --> 00:28:35,649
to walk for thousands of miles later.

590
00:28:35,650 --> 00:28:37,710
Now that you've made up your mind,

591
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:40,910
it's a tough road ahead.

592
00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:44,360
The shoes may be old,

593
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:46,710
but they'll

594
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:49,240
save you some hard time.

595
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:52,630
Thank you.

596
00:29:01,650 --> 00:29:02,800
I

597
00:29:04,650 --> 00:29:05,910
don't need shoes.

598
00:29:14,900 --> 00:29:17,139
(A week later, Wuzhou)

599
00:29:17,140 --> 00:29:25,040
(Flock of sheep, bait, us)

600
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:37,110
What's this?

601
00:29:37,170 --> 00:29:39,040
That's what we're going to fix

602
00:29:39,220 --> 00:29:40,800
before Qiling gets out.

603
00:29:41,370 --> 00:29:43,870
Gosh, that's a lot.

604
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:45,190
It will be solved.

605
00:29:46,090 --> 00:29:47,670
Haixing's reply.

606
00:29:51,940 --> 00:29:55,459
(Wu Xie: My brother buried Niata and
succeeded to the position of Deren.)

607
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:57,019
Zhang Haike has become Deren.

608
00:29:57,020 --> 00:29:58,190
What?

609
00:29:59,020 --> 00:30:00,390
What's going on?

610
00:30:11,810 --> 00:30:13,360
You're going away, Sir?

611
00:30:14,740 --> 00:30:16,000
Mister,

612
00:30:16,700 --> 00:30:17,840
let's

613
00:30:18,130 --> 00:30:20,280
