619
00:30:32,020 --> 00:30:33,600
I wonder if the spiritual retreat

620
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:35,870
will accept a sinner like me.

621
00:30:39,020 --> 00:30:41,520
Even sinners need tea.

622
00:30:54,330 --> 00:30:56,320
I've buried her here

623
00:30:57,260 --> 00:30:59,080
at Snow Peak

624
00:31:00,330 --> 00:31:02,360
