625
00:31:03,650 --> 00:31:05,080
Why don't you let go?

626
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:07,779
How do I let it go?

627
00:31:07,780 --> 00:31:09,259
Just put it

628
00:31:09,260 --> 00:31:10,760
on the table.

629
00:31:22,370 --> 00:31:24,710
I wonder why

630
00:31:25,810 --> 00:31:27,840
young people think so much nowadays.

631
00:31:29,130 --> 00:31:31,760
Repentance and

632
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:33,320
obsession.

633
00:31:35,940 --> 00:31:37,059
I forgot

634
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:38,470
that you're not a young man.

635
00:31:39,370 --> 00:31:40,499
But I'd say

636
00:31:40,500 --> 00:31:43,760
at your age, you've lived in vain.

637
00:31:46,540 --> 00:31:47,840
I understand.

638
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:50,280
You mean

639
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:52,320
I shouldn't think

640
00:31:52,740 --> 00:31:54,240
about how to atone for my sins,

641
00:31:54,850 --> 00:31:57,240
but how to let go of my obsession?

642
00:31:57,850 --> 00:31:59,600
Only when I've unburdened myself

643
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:01,910
