644
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:04,320
will I be able to meditate.

645
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:07,520
Let me get you a job.

646
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:09,800
Take on the position of Deren.

647
00:32:10,980 --> 00:32:13,360
A one-track mind like yours

648
00:32:13,370 --> 00:32:15,390
is perfect for this job.

649
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:23,150
If you want to be Deren,

650
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:27,870
you can't leave here
for the rest of your life.

651
00:32:29,090 --> 00:32:31,190
Unless Zhang Qiling

652
00:32:31,410 --> 00:32:33,150
doesn't need Deren anymore,

653
00:32:33,890 --> 00:32:36,280
you can leave.

654
00:32:38,780 --> 00:32:39,950
Don't worry.

655
00:32:40,410 --> 00:32:43,320
I'll do my duty as Deren.

656
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:46,800
I've been polishing

657
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:48,939
this string of beads for years

658
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,089
but I just can't

659
00:32:50,090 --> 00:32:52,979
get it as round and seamless

660
00:32:52,980 --> 00:32:54,699
as other beads.

661
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:56,190
Later, I realised

662
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:59,190
that the material I'd chosen

663
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:02,169
was the hardest stone to polish.

664
00:33:02,170 --> 00:33:04,430
I think it's fine the way it is.

665
00:33:04,780 --> 00:33:05,950
As Deren,

666
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:09,000
you should always do your best,

667
00:33:09,130 --> 00:33:11,390
but don't be too hard on yourself.

668
00:33:20,220 --> 00:33:21,520
Thank you, Sir.

669
00:33:30,650 --> 00:33:32,110
A man

670
00:33:33,220 --> 00:33:34,499
who's obsessed for decades

671
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:37,240
and finds out it's all a scam.

672
00:33:41,370 --> 00:33:44,240
What is this if not a tragedy?

673
00:33:46,610 --> 00:33:48,320
So I can now understand

674
00:33:49,370 --> 00:33:51,280
why he chose
to go for spiritual practice.

675
00:33:51,890 --> 00:33:54,520
Hope he finds his inner peace soon.

676
00:33:57,300 --> 00:33:59,560
It's not over yet.

677
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:33,160
You've decided to stay here?

678
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:44,160
Haixing,

679
00:34:47,380 --> 00:34:49,030
I've read Wu Xie's letter.

680
00:34:49,820 --> 00:34:52,760
I'm not here to run away.

681
00:34:53,250 --> 00:34:55,160
I'm here to start over.

682
00:34:56,730 --> 00:34:58,769
