692
00:35:32,340 --> 00:35:34,640
You should have your own life.

693
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:40,160
My own life?

694
00:35:40,290 --> 00:35:42,070
Leave me as a burden behind

695
00:35:43,020 --> 00:35:44,430
