from the beginning.

702
00:36:28,340 --> 00:36:29,760
But after all,

703
00:36:32,820 --> 00:36:35,240
I'm the one who got you into this mess.

704
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:38,550
They say

705
00:36:39,250 --> 00:36:41,840
children born
into the Zhang family aren't happy,

706
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:44,390
but I'm different.

707
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:47,240
When I was a kid,

708
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:52,470
no matter how much danger I was in,

709
00:36:52,820 --> 00:36:54,200
no matter how difficult things were,

710
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:56,870
I was never afraid

711
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:00,870
because you were there.

712
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:07,360
Everyone envied me.

713
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:12,200
So at that time, I thought

714
00:37:13,820 --> 00:37:15,360
that when I grow up,

715
00:37:17,290 --> 00:37:19,470
I'll protect you

716
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:21,910
like you protected me.

717
00:37:24,420 --> 00:37:25,550
Unfortunately,

718
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:29,160
I went about it the wrong way.

719
00:37:32,020 --> 00:37:33,760
I know you were wrong,

720
00:37:35,130 --> 00:37:37,120
but I still kept making mistakes
with you.

721
00:37:39,570 --> 00:37:41,720
It's my tolerance
that got you into trouble.

722
00:37:43,210 --> 00:37:44,249
Haixing,

723
00:37:44,250 --> 00:37:45,720
I need your help.

724
00:37:47,210 --> 00:37:49,800
If I'm going to save her,
I have to make a choice.

725
00:37:51,130 --> 00:37:52,430
This is wrong.

726
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:55,680
I've worked so hard for the Zhang family
for so many years,

727
00:37:55,770 --> 00:37:57,289
can't I get a Zanghai Flower

728
00:37:57,290 --> 00:37:58,870
for my life's happiness?

729
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:01,030
You've changed.

730
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:04,360
How come you've become like Zhang Nian?

731
00:38:06,170 --> 00:38:08,680
We've just chosen different paths.

732
00:38:09,060 --> 00:38:11,950
Just like we chose different paths
from the patriarch back then.

733
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:16,499
Now that I've chosen this path,

734
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:17,640
what do you choose?

735
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:23,910
I can't help you.

736
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:32,430
Haixing,

737
00:38:32,860 --> 00:38:34,320
I beg you.

738
00:38:35,210 --> 00:38:37,200
I just need you to help me this once.

739
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:38,720
Just this once.

740
00:38:39,170 --> 00:38:40,280
Okay?

741
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:47,390
We screwed it all up.

742
00:38:51,170 --> 00:38:52,800
You don't have to blame yourself.

743
00:38:53,340 --> 00:38:55,320
I'm the one who didn't do it right.

744
00:38:56,170 --> 00:38:58,120
You've given me more than

745
00:38:59,020 --> 00:39:00,019
