750
00:39:16,690 --> 00:39:17,800
Haike,

751
00:39:19,290 --> 00:39:20,510
I'm leaving.

752
00:39:22,170 --> 00:39:23,510
But this time,

753
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:27,120
