There's still a long way to go.

763
00:40:33,725 --> 00:40:35,235
But I think

764
00:40:35,420 --> 00:40:36,819
it's worth

765
00:40:36,820 --> 00:40:38,470
making an exception.

766
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:44,169
I've read about the Wang family

767
00:40:44,170 --> 00:40:45,590
in the scrolls

768
00:40:45,820 --> 00:40:48,200
from Jila Spiritual Retreat before.

769
00:40:49,210 --> 00:40:50,990
As long as they're around,

770
00:40:51,690 --> 00:40:53,019
the nine families,

771
00:40:53,020 --> 00:40:53,870
the Zhangs,

772
00:40:54,210 --> 00:40:55,070
the Wangs,

773
00:40:55,690 --> 00:40:57,160
guarding the Bronze Door,

774
00:40:57,340 --> 00:40:59,550
